title: Votes cast 19th Jan, 2008 South Carolina Republican primary , South Carolina, 1/19/2008
name: Votes cast 19th Jan, 2008 South Carolina Republican primary , South Carolina, 1/19/2008
description: The data for the map is based on the reports published by South Carolina Election Commission after the 19th Jan, 2008 Republican Presidential Primary. The data consists of those who voted in the Republican primary and those who could vote in the Democratic primary. Since South Carolina has open primaries, the registered voters can vote in either parties primary. Of course, if one votes in the Republican primary, then they cannot vote in the Democratic primary.
